<sect2 id="block-dev-mount">
<title
>Mount Commands</title>
<para
>This tab of the module is used to adjust the icons, the mount commands and the unmount commands.</para>
<para
>The listbox at the top of the module shows every device, an icon for the device, its mount point, mount command and unmount command.</para>
<para
>To change these settings, simply click on the device of your choice.  Several text boxes and buttons will appear at the bottom of the 
